text: haey pitabrakd nasa puok yeung thleab ban angkouy nowkanleng muoychamnuon now leumekh daembi sdab ruengreav phe sa ng . bo nde ilauvnih ( kraoypi mou ham meat klaycha anakneasar) anaknea haey pyeayeam sdab ruengreav noh ke pitchea chuobabrateah nung phkay del now karpar ( tam banh ke) cheaminkhan
